{
  "texts": [
    "We are keen to ask: are there other options?",
    "Four particles.",
    "Let us first answer this question in the case of four particles, where we can consider an arbitrary product of four a, a †, b, or b † 's.",
    "A priori, there are 4 4 = 256 options for such products.",
    "However, many trivially vanish due to (2.3) and its Hermitian conjugate."
  ]
}